data.description: Beautiful Large Colonial in Grafton on 1.4 acres of land, in Eaton Township with Bonus room that could be used as a 5th Bedroom, office, or whatever you want.  There is also a nice sized 3 season sunroom, leading to the huge backyard.  This home has had many updates, including new roof, paint, remolded bathroom upstairs, some new flooring installed, and backyard drains put in to avoid standing water.  The above ground pool will also be staying. This home is over 1800 sq ft, and located on a lot of land.  This is a must see house, and is zoned for residential and commercial!!!!
